cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.NE 

The paper deals with machine learning and deep neural networks, which are typically covered in the categories of cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). The paper specifically focuses on one-shot learning in vision and language tasks, which suggests that it could also be classified under cs.CV (Computer Vision) and cs.CL (Computation and Language). Finally, the paper uses metric learning and external memories, which are techniques commonly used in artificial intelligence, suggesting that it could also be classified under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
